Package: eyesim
Type: Package
Title: Analysis of Eye-Movement Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Bradley", "Buchsbaum", email = "brad.buchsbaum@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for analyzing eye-movement fixation data with a focus on
    computing fixation pattern similarity, density map generation, scanpath
    comparison, and recognition memory paradigms. Implements template-based
    similarity analysis, the MultiMatch algorithm for scanpath comparison,
    cross-recurrence quantification analysis (CRQA), Earth Mover's Distance
    (EMD) based similarity, and latent-space transforms (PCA, CORAL, CCA)
    for density map comparison.
